                    "You kiss her. It feels both out of nowhere and preordained by heaven, like all good kisses."
                "\\"I'm a communist too. I would kiss you but you're my boss and I'm not a fan of uneven power dynamics.\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk writer talk "Your boss? I'm not your boss. I'm a glorified letterbox with a compromised immune system. You can kiss me if you want, Ghost."
                        "[Kiss her]":
                            "You kiss her. It feels both out of nowhere and preordained by heaven, like all good kisses."
                "\\"I'm a communist too. Can I kiss you? I know you're my boss but as a fan of uneven power dynamics I think it'd be hot.\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk writer talk "Your boss? I'm not your boss. I'm a glorified letterbox with a compromised immune system. You can kiss me if you want, Ghost."
                        "[Kiss her]":
                            "You kiss her. It feels both out of nowhere and preordained by heaven, like all good kisses."
                "\\"I'm a communist too. You should rethink some of the aspects of your specific ideology though.\\"":
