                    clear_dialog
                    "She kisses you. It feels both out of nowhere and preordained by heaven, like all good kisses."
                "\\"I'm not a communist. I got kicked in the head by a sheep when I was a baby by the way.\\"":
                    choice:
                        talk writer talk "No. Not a lot of people are in Anglia. Still, you seem okay, for un traître à ta classe."
                        "\\"On train track to ta class. Yup. That's what they always called me.\\" [Nod your head]":
                            "The Pulp Writer smiles, ever so softly."
                            if (roll writer_two_embarrassed_lovely lovely 40):
                                talk lovely talk "She's a little embarrassed for you, but she finds you sweet, far sweeter than most of les petites femmes she meets."
                            else:
                                wait 1000
